title: Templates
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Templates define how a definition for a term is displayed, by default using the html ''&lt;abbr&gt;'' element, e.g.:

`<abbr title="some info">hover me</abbr>`

> <abbr title="some info">hover me</abbr>

Templates for ''dict'' must be specified as global macros accepting the following two parameters:

; dt
: the term
; dd
: the definition

